97
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:08,000
It made a lot of sense to us to pair it with this new Citadel mode.

98
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:15,000
It really is an activity that's geared towards people who love to play together with their friends or with strangers,

99
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:17,000
